Tour of Hayden Lake
description: Race around beautiful Hayden Lake on a challenging 25 mile loop. The road is in great shape which makes this twisting up and down course a lot of fun.
course: Pro 1,2,3s will do three laps. every one else will do 2 Laps. This course is not flat rolling all the time. Beautiful road around the lake. Race starts at 9:00 a.m.
registration: Registration starts morning of at 7:30-8:45 entry fee is $25
directions: Directions from I90. Head north on 95 right on to Lancaster then right on English point. Parking will be right there.
